 & =\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}x}(5x^{6}\ln(x))\\
 & =\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}x}(5x^{6})\ln(x)+5x^{6}\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}x}(\ln(x))\\
 & =30x^{5}\ln(x)+5x^{6}\cdot\frac{1}{x}\\
 & =30x^{5}\ln(x)+5x^{5}\\
